name: Macy_Malo
content:
Macy Malo was a Human female pilot who lived on Tatooine during the Galactic Civil War.
Macy Malo was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Macy Malo was added to the game as part of the "Tusken Army" Heroic Encounter, introduced with the release of the "Chapter 7" update, on November 1, 2007.
